WLC_TERMINATE(3)                                         WLC CORE API FUNCTIONS

NAME

    wlc_terminate - terminate the compositor

SYNOPSIS

    void wlc_terminate(void);

DESCRIPTION

    wlc_terminate() ends any running event loop created with wlc_run(3) and
    terminates the wlc library.

RETURN VALUE

    None.

NOTES

    After the first call to wlc_terminate() any subsequent calls will have no
    effect.

    Calling wlc_terminate() before wlc_init(3) will have no effect.

ALSO SEE

    wlc_init(3), wlc_run(3)
